 Galvatrons tail whipped out to block it and it was cut off in the process. 
Spark shot from it. He howled in pain. His training let him continue on 
blocking it out. Galvatrons saw a blip on his radar. An object Megatron was 
carrying. It was causing a wierd energy to flow from it. He swung  his sword 
at it trying to free it. Any advantage he could get.
